      "content": "but it doesn't feel like \"rest\" or \"self-love.\" it feels like the road just ends here. everything is quiet and empty. it feels like the last stop on the line, like the final exit. why does anyone try so hard to keep driving when the destination is clearly reached and it's just... darkness?",
